translate french main18mcgee_6cc3d260:

    # "I hang up... I guess I'll have to call somebody else."
    "Je raccroche... Je suppose que je vais devoir appeler quelqu'un d'autre."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1977
translate french main18mills_4c0cc5a4:

    # pc "Hi Mrs. Mills. I have something weird to ask you, but can you trust me?"
    pc "Bonjour Mme Mills. J'ai une question bizarre à vous poser, mais pouvez-vous me faire confiance ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1978
translate french main18mills_34eadffe:

    # bs "Haha, of course not. What do you want?"
    bs "Haha, bien sûr que non. Que voulez-vous ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1979
translate french main18mills_e491ccce:

    # pc "Can I send you an address and you come out here and help me with something?"
    pc "Puis-je vous envoyer une adresse pour que vous veniez ici m'aider ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1980
translate french main18mills_1f416382:

    # bs "No, I don't think so. I'm pretty busy today."
    bs "Non, je ne pense pas. Je suis assez occupée aujourd'hui."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1981
translate french main18mills_aaff29fb:

    # bs "Are you in trouble or something?"
    bs "Tu as des ennuis ou quoi ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1982
translate french main18mills_c7b97ec9:

    # pc "No, um... not in trouble."
    pc "Non, euh... pas d'ennuis."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1983
translate french main18mills_4ba39846:

    # bs "Okay, I'll see you at work then."
    bs "D'accord, on se voit au travail alors."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1984
translate french main18mills_9e9e1601:

    # pc "Yeah. Okay."
    pc "Ouais. D'accord."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1985
translate french main18mills_6cc3d260:

    # "I hang up... I guess I'll have to call somebody else."
    "Je raccroche... Je suppose que je vais devoir appeler quelqu'un d'autre."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1993
translate french main18loser_6413d287:

    # pc "Uh... I'm not sure who I would call."
    pc "Euh... Je ne sais pas trop qui j'appellerais."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1994
translate french main18loser_dbacda31:

    # wt "I guess jumping jacks then?"
    wt "Je suppose que ce sera des jumping jacks alors ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1995
translate french main18loser_d46b4e96:

    # pc "Jumping jacks it is."
    pc "Ce sera des jumping jacks."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1998
translate french main18loser_a11e18c1:

    # pc "Why did I have to take my clothes off for this?"
    pc "Pourquoi j'ai dû me déshabiller pour ça ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:1999
translate french main18loser_ebf9e471:

    # wt "It just makes things easier."
    wt "Ça facilite juste les choses."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2000
translate french main18loser_96dadf2b:

    # pc "For who?"
    pc "Pour qui ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2001
translate french main18loser_c4d3505d:

    # wt "Stop asking questions and focus on your heart rate."
    wt "Arrête de poser des questions et concentre-toi sur ton rythme cardiaque."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2004
translate french main18loser_54978e29:

    # wt "You're at 180bpm. You're ready. Here we go."
    wt "Tu es à 180 bpm. Tu es prêt. C'est parti."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2005
translate french main18loser_f2233d53:

    # "I try to say something back, but I'm out of breath and my heart is beating too hard."
    "J'essaie de répondre, mais je suis à bout de souffle et mon cœur bat trop fort."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2006
translate french main18loser_bcb3ff3d:

    # "Then it's too late."
    "Puis c'est trop tard."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2009
translate french main18loser_77047fcf:

    # "The warehouse and everything else disappear, and I'm falling through space."
    "L'entrepôt et tout le reste disparaissent, et je tombe dans le vide."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2016
translate french main18d_200925de:

    # "At first everything is dark, I'm spinning, and I can't tell which way is up or down, or even if it matters."
    "Au début, tout est noir, je tourne sur moi-même, et je ne sais pas où est le haut ni le bas, ni même si ça a de l'importance."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2025
translate french main18d_40873d37:

    # "Then the darkness slowly starts to form colors that swirl and mix around me."
    "Puis l'obscurité commence lentement à former des couleurs qui tourbillonnent et se mélangent autour de moi."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2028
translate french main18d_7c8ff3d9:

    # "There's a light from somewhere ahead and I'm being pulled towards it, like through some kaleidoscopic tunnel."
    "Il y a une lumière quelque part devant moi et je suis attiré vers elle, comme à travers un tunnel kaléidoscopique."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2031
translate french main18d_52b9925f:

    # "The light at the end of the tunnel grows bigger and bigger."
    "La lumière au bout du tunnel devient de plus en plus grande."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2032
translate french main18d_2fdeacbc:

    # "And I begin to doubt. Is all of this even real? Am I actually going to another world?"
    "Et je commence à douter. Tout cela est-il seulement réel ? Est-ce que je vais vraiment dans un autre monde ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2033
translate french main18d_f057c091:

    # "Or am I just dead and all of this is all being caused by my last dying gasp flooding my brain with chemicals?"
    "Ou suis-je simplement mort et tout cela est-il causé par mon dernier souffle qui inonde mon cerveau de substances chimiques ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2036
translate french main18d_47b48d88:

    # "The light is blinding as it washes over me."
    "La lumière est aveuglante alors qu’elle m’enveloppe."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2037
translate french main18d_5064f0cf:

    # "If this is death, at least I had a good time before I died."
    "Si c'est ça, la mort, au moins j'ai passé un bon moment avant de mourir."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2042
translate french main18d_b6f2c352:

    # "Then the light is gone, and all is dark once again."
    "Puis la lumière disparaît, et tout redevient sombre."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2043
translate french main18d_9f91f57e:

    # "And cold. So cold."
    "Et froid. Tellement froid."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2044
translate french main18d_72fee9f9:

    # "It takes me a moment to realize that everything is cold because I am naked."
    "Il me faut un moment pour comprendre que tout est froid parce que je suis nu."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2045
translate french main18d_3494c31e:

    # "And everything is dark because my eyes are closed."
    "Et que tout est sombre parce que mes yeux sont fermés."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2046
translate french main18d_eaa77573:

    # "I open them slowly..."
    "Je les ouvre lentement..."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2049
translate french main18d_e7caae0f:

    # "It's real."
    "C'est réel."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2050
translate french main18d_0c9a8c16:

    # "Everything is a little blurry as my eyes still have not adjusted, but it definitely looks different."
    "Tout est un peu flou, mes yeux ne s’étant pas encore adaptés, mais ça a clairement l’air différent."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2053
translate french main18d_c9534d15:

    # "Sounds different. A quiet I've never experienced before."
    "Ça sonne différemment. Un silence que je n’ai jamais connu auparavant."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2054
translate french main18d_dc605673:

    # "It smells different. Crisp, fresh."
    "Ça sent différemment. Vif, frais."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2057
translate french main18d_1414b67c:

    # "No, I'm definitely not in Skyhill anymore."
    "Non, je ne suis définitivement plus à Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2060
translate french main18d_ec5da7c6:

    # "There is somebody else here. I hear footsteps approaching."
    "Il y a quelqu’un d’autre ici. J’entends des pas qui s’approchent."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2063
translate french main18d_514b24f3:

    # "They're on a horse. I rub my eyes, trying to get them to focus."
    "Ils sont à cheval. Je me frotte les yeux, essayant de les faire focaliser."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2064
translate french main18d_1fb664f0:

    # "Familiar Voice" "Hello there! Are you okay?"
    "Familiar Voice" "Bonjour ! Ça va ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2067
translate french main18d_841466ea:

    # "I recognize that voice... who is that?"
    "Je reconnais cette voix... qui est-ce ?"

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2068
translate french main18d_d510b63b:

    # "Familiar Voice" "Where are your clothes, sir? You'll freeze to death like that."
    "Familiar Voice" "Où sont vos vêtements, monsieur ? Vous allez mourir de froid comme ça."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2071
translate french main18d_33ab6d2e:

    # "Familiar Voice" "I have a cloak you can use. Let me help you."
    "Familiar Voice" "J'ai une cape que vous pouvez utiliser. Laissez-moi vous aider."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2072
translate french main18d_0d0b58f2:

    # "Then it becomes clear who this is..."
    "Puis je comprends enfin qui c'est..."

# game/Scenes/Other/main18.rpy:2076
translate french main18d_b28989b0:

    # pc "Mom?"
    pc "Maman ?"

